        // The median $M_1$ must be one of $a_0, \dots, a_{2n-1}$.
        // The median $M_2$ must be one of $a_0, \dots, a_{2n-1}$.
        //
        // The number of elements in $C_1$ that are $\le M_1$ is $k_1+1$.
        // The number of elements in $C_2$ that are $\le M_2$ is $k_2+1$.
